1. Ja *pratim* tvoj račun na društvenim mrežama. (I am *following* your social media account.)
2. Ti *pratiš* moje upute za pripremu jela. (You *follow* my instructions for cooking.)
3. Oni *prate* vesti na televiziji svakog dana. (They *watch* news on TV every day.)
4. Mi *pratimo* trendove u modi. (We *follow* fashion trends.)
5. Vi *pratite* putokaze do muzeja. (You *follow* the signs to the museum.)
6. Studenti *prate* predavanja na fakultetu. (Students *attend* lectures at university.)
7. Mama me uvek *prati* u stopu kada sam u gradu. (Mom always *follows* me closely when I'm in the city.)
8. Kada se vozim biciklom, uvek *pratim* saobraćajna pravila. (When I'm cycling, I always *follow* traffic rules.)
9. Učiteljica *prati* napredak svakog učenika posebno. (The teacher *monitors* the progress of each student individually.)
10. Fudbalski navijači *prate* svoj tim na svim utakmicama. (Football fans *support* their team at all matches.)